=={{anchor|Adaptaplug}}RadioShack Adaptaplug==<!-- This section is linked from [[Adaptaplug]] -->
[[RadioShack]] sold a line of adapter plugs for universal [[AC adapters]]. Each "Adaptaplug" had a single-letter code, but did not provide any other official designation, nor did RadioShack publish the complete specifications and tolerances on barrel and pin dimensions. RadioShack's web site listed the diameters to the nearest 0.1&nbsp;mm, and sometimes differs slightly from the official [[EIAJ connector|EIAJ RC-5320A]] standard dimensions.{{clarify |date=September 2016 |reason=It's not clear if the RadioShack web site listed the diameters or the actual diameters differ slightly from the official EIAJ RC-5320A standard dimensions.}} This list may include some parts RadioShack has discontinued but are retained here for completeness.<ref>[http://support.radioshack.com/support_tutorials/batteries/pwrgde-2H.htm Adaptaplug System; RadioShack.]</ref>

